subject: feat(data): replace demo dataset with comprehensive tech industry data
body:
Replace the 40-node demo dataset with a 109-node, 149-arc dataset
covering major tech companies, executives, founders, acquisitions,
legal cases, partnerships, supply chain relationships, and competition.

Also fixes a pre-existing bug in queryEngine compare evaluator where
the builder path preserved camelCase property keys but the evaluator
only lowercased the data side, causing mismatches on camelCase keys
like `marketCap`.

Tags: demo-data, seed, query-engine, bugfix
